                    If you find it inconvenient to complete all of these questions,
                    you are welcome to upload responses from other participants and modify them as appropriate.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="col-auto mb-4 pb-2 d-flex align-items-end gap-2">
                    <input asp-for="LoadId" type="number" class="form-control" style="width:110px;" />
                    <button type="submit" asp-page-handler="Load" class="btn btn-primary px-4">Load answers by ID</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

